<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idab809fcd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s9591"><num value="9591">§ 9591.</num><heading> Utilities: proceeds from overseas operations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">During actual or threatened hostilities, proceeds from operating a public utility in connection with operations of the Air Force or the Space Force in the field overseas are available for that utility until the close of the fiscal year following that in which they are received.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idab809fce-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/578">70A Stat. 578</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/116/283/dA/tIX/s923/e/6">Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title IX, § 923(e)(6)</ref>, <date date="2021-01-01">Jan. 1, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/3816">134 Stat. 3816</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
